Invocation Name: baby names
des:
If you are expecting a baby and thinking about a name I can suggest girls and boys names. It's very simple, you can ask me by saying:

- Give me a boy name.
- Give me a girl name.
- Suggest a boy name.
- Suggest a girl name.
